data.description: Motivated Seller bring all offers on this Spectacular single story in the highly sought-after community of Park Trails in the heart of Princeton! Designer touches throughout include decorative lighting, rich wood flooring, vaulted ceilings, and a spacious open floor plan that is great for entertaining family and friends complete with two living and dining areas.  Eat-in kitchen with granite countertops, tiled backsplash, SS appliances, updated hardware & an abundance of cabinetry.  The family room is light and bright with a door leading to the large covered patio and generous backyard.  The private primary suite offers WIC, a garden tub, a separate shower,  & custom vanity with H+H sinks.  Secondary bedrooms are spacious in size and split from primary.  Situated on a corner lot across the street from the community park.
